                  </p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Web of Science (SCI, SSCI, ESCI)</li>
                    <li>Scopus-indexed international journals</li>
                    <li>Impact factor & CiteScore evaluation</li>
                    <li>Journal ranking & quartile (Q1–Q4) analysis</li>
