              </li>

              <li class="tool-item">
                <div class="tool-header">
                  <img src="images/UGC-Care-Journals-3.png" alt="ABDC Journals" class="tool-icon">
                  <div>
                    <span>Academic Ranking Lists</span>
                    <small>ABDC, Annexure & UGC CARE</small>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tool-body">
                  <p>
                    Academic journal ranking lists guide researchers in selecting credible
